author: Connor Creates
description:
Sign up to Milanote for free with no time-limit: https://milanote.com/itsconnorcreates

It was surprisingly easy to make this natural pine tree soda (spoiler alert: it does indeed taste like Sprite!). All you need is:
- a glass bottle/jar that can withstand pressurization
- pine needles (from a safe pine tree variety)
- sugar (or sugar substitute) 
- natural spring water 

Also if you made it to the end of the video and heard the fun news about the hats that I'm making, you can check out my website here (https://www.connorcreates.com/) to sign up for exclusive early access!

Come say hi on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/itsconnorcreates
And subscribe here on YT: youtube.com/@itsConnorCreates

thanks for watching this video, I truly appreciate your support! :)
title: I Tried Turning a Tree into Soda
